short_description: chubbsafes is a hardware store based in palembang, indonesia.
long_description: we pride ourselves on making security a part of your everyday life. chubbsafes is one of the oldest safes brand in the world. trusted the world over, the chubbsafes solutions have been providing protection around the globe for people, cash and valuables for almost 200 years. the chubb brothers started the company by designing and manufacturing safes and locks for banking and financial institutions. chubb lock & safe company of new zealand was founded. 1965 josiah parkes & sons ltd. became a member of chubb group. 1984 chubb & sons lock and safe company ltd became part of the racal electronics group. all products continued under the registered name of chubb & sons lock and safe ltd. 1986 the strength of chubb was acknowledged by racal when the group of companies was renamed to racal-chubb products ltd. 1992 the chubb group of companies was registered on the london stock exchange as chubb security plc. 1997 williams holding acquired chubb security plc. and structured every chubb company throughout the world. 2000 chubb safes marketed by global security provider gunnebo.

generated_description: chubbsafes, legally known as chubbsafes thailand co. ltd., based in warsaw, masovian voivodeship, is a company specializing in the design and manufacture of certified safes and cabinets. the company's products are used globally, with a strong presence in europe, africa, and asia. chubbsafes offers a range of security solutions including graded safes, fireproof safes, deposit safes, and storage cabinets. these products are designed to protect private valuables, cash, documents, and technical equipment from burglary, fire, and explosives. chubbsafes is known for its robustness, reliability, and modern designs, and its products are rigorously tested by international accreditation bodies to ensure high levels of security. the company's customer base includes householders, small commercial shops, large retail environments, jewelry stores, and major financial institutions.
